					<h3>Choose the video that you want you insert thumbnail</h3>
					<img class="tutorial-image" src="~/first_step.png" />
					<p>We recommend .mp4 file format because it's the most common format for video. Tiktok also prefer mp4 file
						format to others.</p>
					<h3>Choosing the thumbnail image that you want to insert into the video</h3>
					<img class="tutorial-image" src="~/second_step.png" />
					<p>You should choose the common image format such as .png, .jpeg, jpg with high quality and eye catching
						enough to catch the attention from viewers. The recommended image resolution is 1080 x 1920. This is also
