						<p>We recommend using the .jpg, .png, or .jpeg formats. However, other formats should work as
							well.</p>
						<h3>6. Does it also work for Instagram and other platform?</h3>
						<p>Yes, this will also work for other platforms. However, these platforms support cover natively so we usually don't need them.</p>
						<h3>7. What if tiktok support cover someday? Would this website be useful then?</h3>
						<p>Then you are good to use the Tiktok way instead of using this website. However, it's not likely for them to support native cover soon since they had this functionality but then deleted it for no particular reason.</p>
